Package org.eng.storage

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IDeleteableItemStorage<ITEM>  
    IFieldedItemStorage<ITEM>
    Extends the super interface to define methods allowing search for items by item field values.
    IItemStorage<ITEM>  
    INamedItemStorage<ITEM>
    Stores items that have names and allows search on those names and the item fields via the super class.
    INamedSerializableStorage<SITEM extends Serializable,METADATA>
    Extends the ISerializableStorage to enable easy assigning of a name to an item in storage.
    IReadOnlyStorage<ITEM>
    Defines the operations on a storage instance that are independent of the items being stored.
    IReferencingStringSetStorage<SETITEM extends NamedStringSet,ITEM>
    Models a storage instance that stores items and a set of ids referencing those items.
    ISerializableStorage<SITEM extends Serializable,METADATA>
    Captures methods used for storage of a serializable Java type with associated metadata on which searches can be performed.
    IStringSetStorage
    Interface to needed to store named lists of strings (usually item ids, but could be anything).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDeleteableItemStorage<ITEM>
    Provides simple implementations of methods that can be implemented using sub-class implementations.
    AbstractFiledItemStorage<ITEM>
    Provides the base interface implementation only requires the subclass to provide a few methods.
    AbstractReadOnlyStorage<ITEM>  
    FieldValues
    Holds key/value pairs that specify the values of fields of a java object stored in a NoSQL db.
    JSONFiledItemStorage<ITEM>
    Provides a limited ability to store Java objects as serialized JSON objects.
    NamedStringSet  
    SerializedFiledItemStorage<ITEM extends Serializable>
    Provides a limited ability to store Java objects as java serialization.
    StoredItemByIDIterable<ITEM>
    An iterable over items referenced in an IItemStorage instance.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    StorageException
